     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Forest theme. Dark nature-inspired
         palette: deep forest green (#1C2318) background with muted green
         (#6A9F5B) accents and warm brown (#C8A56A) highlights. Unique
         and restful for long editing sessions.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in ForestTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

